      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine that requires immediate attention and a transmission that hesitates between gears. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches and paint fading, while the interior has several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car would be best suited as a major restoration project or a source for parts.",
