      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it rolled off the lot yesterday! I have taken such good care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. There's not a single flaw to be found. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel!",
