    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S in pristine Montego Blue. This example features the legendary 13B-REW twin-rotor engine with perfectly synchronized sequential turbochargers, maintaining factory-spec boost pressure across the entire powerband. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its original 50/50 weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension. Performance is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with verified compression results and zero vacuum system degradation, this is a rare opportunity to own a pinnacle of 90s Japanese engineering in its most authentic form.",
      "price": 43500.0,
