    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-condition vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original deep-gloss finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. The interior is a total time-capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule by certified master technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road salt or fluid seepage. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that has been pampered since day one. Includes all original keys, owner's manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service receipts.",
